=== What This Document Governs

This document governs decisions made by students regarding the personal use of alchemical and spagyric preparations they have independently produced in their own workspaces using materials they have independently sourced. It does not govern the curriculum's educational content, which describes historical and traditional methods without instructing or endorsing their consumptive use.

